=== How AI Assistants Use This
<how-ai-assistants-use-this>
When you ask Claude Code to "add a discount field to orders", it:

+ #strong[Searches] the catalog to find the Order entity
+ #strong[Analyzes] existing patterns in your project
+ #strong[Generates] MDL that matches your conventions
+ #strong[Validates] the change won't break existing logic
+ #strong[Applies] the change and shows you the diff

```sql
/** AI discovers the entity */
DESCRIBE ENTITY Sales.Order;

/**
 * AI generates the modification.
 * Adds discount percentage applied to order (0-100).
 */
ALTER ENTITY Sales.Order
    ADD ATTRIBUTE DiscountPercent: Decimal DEFAULT 0;

/**
 * AI updates the total calculation microflow
 * (based on analysis of existing patterns)
 */
```

