=== Catalog Management
<catalog-management>
The catalog is a SQLite database that caches project metadata for fast querying:

```bash
# Refresh catalog (within MDL commands)
mxcli -p app.mpr -c "REFRESH CATALOG"           # Quick refresh
mxcli -p app.mpr -c "REFRESH CATALOG FULL"      # Full rebuild with refs
mxcli -p app.mpr -c "REFRESH CATALOG FULL FORCE" # Force rebuild

# Query catalog tables
mxcli -p app.mpr -c "SELECT Name FROM CATALOG.MICROFLOWS LIMIT 10"
mxcli -p app.mpr -c "SHOW CATALOG TABLES"
```

Catalog is cached in `.mxcli/catalog.db` next to the MPR file.

=== Debug and Advanced Tools
<debug-and-advanced-tools>
```bash
# Dump raw BSON data for debugging widget/page issues
mxcli dump-bson -p app.mpr --doc "Module.PageName"

# Extract widget templates from a project
mxcli extract-templates -p app.mpr --output ./templates/

